Bitcoin Price Strategy Analysis & Backtesting
This project showcases a full pipeline for backtesting a Bitcoin trading strategy using historical market data. Built for freelance and portfolio use, it demonstrates data handling, strategy logic, and performance analysis using Python libraries like Backtrader and PyFolio.

ğŸ¯ Objectives
Load and clean BTC-USD historical data

Apply a custom trading strategy (Moving Average Crossover)

Backtest using the Backtrader engine

Analyze results using PyFolio for performance metrics

Export key performance charts and logs

